Step 1:
  Install the conda environment in conda_env/mpas_testing.yaml
  Use this command to install: conda env create -f mpas_testing.yaml
    or
  Install a recent verion of python 3 and pyyaml

Step 2:
  Modify config.yaml

Step 3:
  Run create_idea.py

Step 4:
  Change to case directory and run `bash run.sh`
